### 사용자 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 사용자 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "javakim",
  "password": "password123"
}

